(143, 'R143', 'Southern Pacific Third & Townsend', '', 'The Southern Pacific Third and Townsend St. Depot located in San Francisco has been replicated by award-winning SP Prototype Modeler Mark Brown.  Mark has replicated the depot, platform tracks, and the fourth street tower in his garage.  The diorama is almost to scale and features custom double slip switches and crossovers to match SP prototype.  All structures built so far are completely scratch built.  Digitrax DCC.', 'HO', NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Digitrax DCC', 1, NULL, NULL, '', 'Mark', 'Brown', '(916) 872-8499', '', '', '101 Roadrunner Court', 'Roseville', 'CA', '', '', NULL),
