(167, 'R167', 'Sierra Railroad', '', 'Multi - deck layout with over 10 scale miles of Sierra Railroad mainline trackage plus Interchanges with SP and ATSF in Oakdale, Pickering Lumber Co at Standard, WSLCo in Tuolumne and the Hetch Hetchy RR at Hetch Hetchy Jct. Prototypical operations based on 1955 prototype. Base scenery is about 90% done with some finished scenery. Most structures are in place. Layout designed for operations.', 'HO HOn3', '', '', '50%', '22 X 65', '', '', '', 'Easy DCC', 2, 'N', 'N', 'http://www.sierrarailroad55.com', 'John', 'Zach', '(209) 625-5609', '', '', '17921 Bononza Dr.', 'Twain Harte', 'CA', '', '', 1),
