(22, 'L404', 'MODESTO', '2011-07-06 00:00:00', '2011-07-06 00:00:00', 'Two of the layouts on this tour were built by professional railroaders and one is undergoing a major expansion giving this trip a unique flavor.', 1, '', 0.00, 0, '', 0, 0),
