(34, 'L701', 'SF BAY AREA GARDEN RAILWAYS', '2011-07-09 08:00:00', '2011-07-09 17:00:00', 'This tour will visit six really interesting garden railways in the San Francisco Bay Area. Each of these railways features well built outdoor railroads in garden settings that are sure to be of great interest to those into gardening as well as garden railway aficionados. Lunch will be on your own from a selection of fast food restaurants available at a local shopping area   ', 1, '', 0.00, 0, '0', 0, 0);
