(64, 'P521', 'SOUTHERN PACIFIC SHOPS TOUR - CSRM', '2011-07-07 00:00:00', '2011-07-07 00:00:00', 'Our tour will begin in the auditorium of the Museum with a presentation on the history of <b><font color="red">..... WHAT ....</font></b> and will continue on to nearby shops.  Although the Museum is fully ADA compliant and anyone can attend the lecture portion of the tour, the shops are a former railroad and current equipment support facility for the Museum and as such not suitable for people with mobility issues.', 1, '', 0.00, 0, '0', 0, 0),
